snippet.title: The Sims 3 Island Paradise Producer Walkthrough
snippet.description: Discover adventure in The Sims 3 Island Paradise with the release of the brand new Producer Walkthrough video! Explore the sunny shores and glistening waters of Isla Paradiso. Learn how your Sims can build and customize houseboats and resorts. Plus, see Sims dive under water and explore the ocean floor. The Sims 3 Island Paradise Expansion Pack is available June 25, 2013.
